No. 09-1526. James L. Martin, Petitioner v. Delaware Law School of Widener University, et al. 562 U.S. 948, 131 S. Ct. 180,

178 L. Ed. 2d 244,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7753. October 4, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.

Justice Alito took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 304 Fed. Appx. 29.
